# Docker & CI

## Local infra
```bash
docker compose up -d postgres redis   # DB + cache only
npm run dev:api                       # API on host (hot reload)
```

## Files
- `docker-compose.yml` — postgres, redis, api (production image)
- `docker-compose.dev.yml` — api volume mount override
- `docker/Dockerfile.api` — runs `prisma migrate deploy` then `node src/index.js`
- `ops/nginx/nginx.conf` — TLS + WebSocket proxy stub
- `ops/secrets/` — JWT keys (gitignored); generate via `npm run generate:jwt-keys`

## CI (`.github/workflows/ci.yml`)
Runs on **every push** and **every pull request** (all branches).
1. lint + lint:i18n
2. api job: postgres service → migrate → seed → test
3. build dashboard, pos, kds

## Env templates
Never commit secrets. Update `apps/*/.env.example` when adding variables.

## Production deploy (later phases)
API image push → SSH → `docker compose pull && docker compose up -d --no-deps api`
